 The UI of the app has a sidebar on the left and a main content area on the right.

In the sidebar, there are 5 sections:
- New Project
- Recent
- Learn to Play
- Lesson Store
- Project Templates

The main content area has a large blue button in the center. The text on the button is "Empty Project". Below the button, there is a text field that says "Create an empty project". Next to the text field, there is a blue button that says "Choose".

In the bottom left corner of the window, there is a button that says "Details".